text: The 2019 GP de Plouay featured as the twentieth round of the 2019 UCI Women's World Tour and was held on 31 August 2019, in Plouay, France. The race was held one day before the men's Bretagne Classic. ==Teams== 128 riders from 22 teams started the race.
